Check if interactive logging is enabled.

Source: R/autogen-config.R
config_is_interactive_logging_enabled.Rd

To switch between writing logs to stdout and absl.logging, you may use keras.config.enable_interactive_logging() and keras.config.disable_interactie_logging().

config_is_interactive_logging_enabled()

Value

Boolean, True if interactive logging is enabled, and False otherwise.

See also

  • https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/keras/config/is_interactive_logging_enabled

Other io utils: config_disable_interactive_logging(), config_enable_interactive_logging()
